OL,3,COnline grooming crimes reach record
OL,4,Clevels, NSPCC says
OL,6,FOnline grooming crimes have reached
OL,7,Frecord levels in the UK, with more
OL,8,Fthan 7,000 offences recorded by police
OL,9,Fover the last year for the first time,
OL,10,Fthe NSPCC has said.
OL,12,FThe children's charity said the
OL,13,Ffigures, provided by 45 UK police
OL,14,Fforces, showed that 7,062 sexual
OL,15,Fcommunication with a child offences
OL,16,Fwere recorded in 2023-24, a rise of
OL,17,F89% since 2017-18, when the offence
OL,18,Ffirst came into force.
