OL,3,COnline grooming crimes reach record
OL,4,Clevels, NSPCC says
OL,6,FIt said there is currently too much
OL,7,Ffocus on acting after harm has taken
OL,8,Fplace, rather than being proactive to
OL,9,Fensure the design of social media
OL,10,Fplatforms does not contribute to abuse.
OL,12,FThe charity has also called on the
OL,13,FGovernment to do more to disrupt child
OL,14,Fsexual abuse in private messages.
OL,16,FSir Peter Wanless, NSPCC chief
OL,17,Fexecutive, said: "One year since the
OL,18,FOnline Safety Act became law and we
OL,19,Fare still waiting for tech companies
OL,20,Fto make their platforms safe for
OL,21,Fchildren.
