OL,6,F"We need ambitious regulation by Ofcom
OL,7,Fwho must significantly strengthen
OL,8,Ftheir current approach to make
OL,9,Fcompanies address how their products
OL,10,Fare being exploited by offenders.
OL,12,F"It is clear that much of this abuse
OL,13,Fis taking place in private messaging,
OL,14,Fwhich is why we also need the
OL,15,FGovernment to strengthen the Online
OL,16,FSafety Act to give Ofcom more legal
OL,17,Fcertainty to tackle child sexual abuse
OL,18,Fon the likes of Snapchat and WhatsApp."
